Presumably this could entail a 3G or even 3.5G HSDPA iPhone for European
markets due to get the iPhone by the end of the year, or even the
addition of more memory - imagine a 16Gb or even 32Gb iPhone, unlikely
though those will be this year mainly due to the high cost of 16 or 32Gb
